---
import Shop from '@/layouts/Shop.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '@/components/astro/Breadcrumb.astro';
import { tenant } from '@/config/tenant';
---

<Shop
  title={`Terms of Service | ${tenant.name}`}
  description={`Terms and conditions for using ${tenant.name}, Europe's premium nicotine pouch shop.`}
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <section class="bg-background text-foreground">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Terms of Service' }]} />

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none
        prose-headings:text-foreground prose-p:text-muted-foreground
        prose-a:text-primary prose-strong:text-foreground
        prose-li:text-muted-foreground prose-hr:border-border">

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-yellow-500/20 bg-yellow-500/5 p-4 mb-8 not-prose">
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-400">
            <strong>Note:</strong> These terms are under review by our legal team and may be updated.
            Last revised: March 2026.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">Effective date: 26 March 2026</p>

        <h2>1. General Terms</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the {tenant.name} website
          located at {tenant.domain} ("Site") and all related services, including ordering,
          account management, and community features. By accessing or using the Site, you
          agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, you must not use the Site.
        </p>
        <p>
          {tenant.name} reserves the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes will be
          posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of the Site
          after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least <strong>18 years of age</strong> (or the legal age for purchasing
          nicotine products in your jurisdiction, whichever is higher) to use the Site and place
          orders. By creating an account or placing an order, you confirm that you meet this age
          requirement.
        </p>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to request proof of age at any time and to cancel orders where
          age verification cannot be completed.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Orders and Pricing</h2>
        <p>
          All prices on the Site are displayed in euros ({tenant.currencyCode}) and include
          applicable taxes unless otherwise stated. Prices are subject to change without notice,
          but changes will not affect orders that have already been confirmed.
        </p>
        <p>
          An order is considered confirmed once you receive an order confirmation email. We
          reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order for reasons including but not limited
          to: product availability, pricing errors, suspected fraud, or failure to meet
          eligibility requirements.
        </p>
        <p>
          Payment is processed securely through our payment provider at checkout. We do not
          store your payment card details on our servers.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
        <p>
          We ship to countries within the European Union. Delivery times are estimates and
          may vary depending on your location and carrier conditions. Typical delivery is
          2-5 business days after dispatch.
        </p>
        <p>
          Free shipping is available on orders over &euro;{tenant.freeShippingThreshold}.
          Shipping costs for orders below this threshold are calculated and displayed at checkout.
        </p>
        <p>
          Risk of loss and title for products pass to you upon delivery. If a package is lost
          or damaged during transit, please contact our support team within 14 days of the
          expected delivery date.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Returns and Refunds</h2>
        <p>
          Due to the nature of nicotine products and health regulations, we can only accept
          returns of unopened, undamaged products in their original packaging within 14 days
          of delivery.
        </p>
        <p>
          To initiate a return, contact our support team at {tenant.supportEmail}. Refunds
          will be processed to your original payment method within 10 business days of receiving
          the returned product.
        </p>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to refuse returns that do not meet these conditions or that show
          signs of tampering.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on the Site &mdash; including text, graphics, logos, images, product
          descriptions, and software &mdash; is the property of {tenant.name} or its licensors
          and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any
          content on the Site without prior written permission. Product names and brand logos
          belong to their respective owners.
        </p>

        <h2>7. User Accounts and Conduct</h2>
        <p>
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials
          and for all activity that occurs under your account. You agree to notify us
          immediately of any unauthorized access.
        </p>
        <p>
          You agree not to: use the Site for any unlawful purpose; submit false or misleading
          information; attempt to interfere with the Site's operation; resell products purchased
          on the Site without authorization; or post abusive, offensive, or harmful content in
          community features.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, {tenant.name} shall not be liable for any
          indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of
          profits or revenues, whether incurred directly or indirectly, arising from your use
          of the Site or products purchased through it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our total liability for any claim arising from these Terms or your use of the Site
          shall not exceed the amount you paid for the specific order giving rise to the claim.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Governing Law and Disputes</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Sweden.
          Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Site shall be resolved
          through the courts of Sweden, without prejudice to any mandatory consumer protection
          provisions in your country of residence that may apply.
        </p>
        <p>
          For EU consumers: you may also use the European Commission's Online Dispute Resolution
          platform at <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at
          <a href={`mailto:${tenant.supportEmail}`}>{tenant.supportEmail}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Shop>
